>\n                    <p>Versatile dumbbells for strength training at home.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Apex Sports Gear</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <div class=\"about-text\">\n                    <p>Apex Sports Gear was founded with a passion for sports and a commitment to quality. We believe that the right equipment can make all the difference in an athlete's journey. Our products are meticulously designed and rigorously tested to ensure they meet the highest standards of performance, durability, and comfort. From the casual enthusiast to the seasoned professional, we equip you to excel.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"about-image\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/4169e1/ffffff?text=Our+Workshop\" alt=\"Our Workshop\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-content\">\n                <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                    <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                        <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                        <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                        <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                        <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                        <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                        <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n\n                        <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                    </form>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                    <p><strong>Apex Sports Gear Headquarters</strong></p>\n                    <p>123 Victory Lane</p>\n                    <p>Sports City, SC 98765</p>\n                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@apexsportsgear.com</p>\n                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Sports Gear. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}